thread.title: Southwest plane makes emergency landing in Philly, damage to exterior

title: Southwest plane makes emergency landing in Philly, damage to exterior
text:
Southwest plane makes emergency landing in Philly, damage to exterior 4:26pm EDT - 00:45 
A Southwest Airlines airplane en route to Dallas made an emergency landing at Philadelphia International Airport on Tuesday after an engine exploded inflight breaking a window, local media reported. Rough Cut (no reporter narration).
